---
title: Chicken Laksa with Noodles and Yellow Pepper
description: Winner winner, chicken laksa dinner. The original laksa recipe is such a hit with our customers that we thought it’d be foolish not to give it a ‘Rapid’ makeover. If you’re in the mood for a soup that is a little bit different, then this creamy and comforting chicken laksa with a spicy noodle broth is the perfect thing to cook this evening.
